name: wBoost
overview:
wBoost is based in Palo Alto, California they aim to bring the relevant services of a corporate interactive agency to small and medium businesses with a price they can afford.

wBoost believes that Online Promotion is one of the most vital tools to the success of all businesses around the world. Everyday there is a new way to acquire and retain new customers via the internet.

wBoost can assist their customers with Web Designing, Web Development, Online Promotion, Search Engine Optimization, Search Engine Marketing, Web Hosting and Email Marketing.

Through their strategic partnership with Constant Contact they have the ability to help their customers utilize one of the worlds leading Email, Event Marketing and Surveying tools.
